# File Structure Guidelines

## Core Files
- `lib/main.dart`: Application entry point
- `lib/app_theme.dart`: Global theme configuration
- `lib/routes.dart`: App navigation routes

## Feature Modules
Each feature should have its own directory with these components:
- `lib/photo_editor/`: Photo editing functionality
- `lib/journal/`: Good things journal functionality
- `lib/tea_tracker/`: Bubble tea tracking functionality
- `lib/settings/`: App settings functionality

## Shared Components
- `lib/shared/`: Reusable widgets and utilities
  - `app_colors.dart`: Color constants
  - `app_text_styles.dart`: Typography styles
  - `glass_card_widget.dart`: Frosted glass effect widget

## Models
- `lib/models/`: Data models
  - Model classes should be defined in their own files
  - Follow naming convention: `model_name.dart`

## Example Structure
```
lib/
├── main.dart
├── app_theme.dart
├── routes.dart
├── models/
│   ├── edited_photo.dart
│   ├── journal_entry.dart
│   ├── tea_record.dart
│   └── user_profile.dart
├── photo_editor/
│   ├── photo_editor_screen.dart
│   └── photo_editor_controller.dart
├── journal/
│   ├── journal_screen.dart
│   └── journal_controller.dart
├── tea_tracker/
│   ├── tea_tracker_screen.dart
│   └── tea_tracker_controller.dart
├── settings/
│   ├── settings_screen.dart
│   └── settings_controller.dart
└── shared/
    ├── app_colors.dart
    ├── app_text_styles.dart
    └── glass_card_widget.dart
```